search_results.title: OUR STORY | Woamy | Biofoam
search_results.snippet: "Woamy", a spinout from Aalto University, was conceived from the insights gained during the Foamwood research project.

search_results.title: Woamy's biofoam to redefine sustainable packaging
search_results.snippet: Founded on over a decade of scientific research, Woamy is on a mission to revolutionise packaging with fully bio-based, biodegradable and recyclable solutions.

search_results.title: Woamy
search_results.snippet: Woamy is revolutionizing the packaging industry with its innovative biofoam technology, developed from a decade of scientific research at Aalto University.
